data.description: Great opportunity to own this 3 Bedroom, 1.5 Bath Colonial in the Lee-Harvard Community!  On the first level, this home offers a spacious living room, dining room, and kitchen. Second floor has 3 bedrooms and a full bath. The lower level has a finished area, which is great from entertaining and/or gaming. Do not miss your opportunity, schedule your showing today!
